configurar a ligacao do tux4 Ã  vlan 1:
ifconfig eth1 172.16.61.253/24

ligar a porta:
echo 1 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward
echo 0 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/icmp_echo_ignore_broadcast

ifconfig

